<b><MARQUEE><font size="5"> WELL HELLO THERE </MARQUEE></font> 
<p> Hi! We are Happy that you have joined our CV making website.This webiste helps you build your CV or you can say a digital CV, where your specialities,skills and work experiences are processed online into a single whole.This Digital CV contains the same information as a regular version.The difference is that they are sub divided over different pages or page sections.More People are switching over to create a digital CV.One of the reason is that your Curricullum Vitae isnt available to just a single person: instead a potentially interested party or company can take a look at your information as well.Our website has companies registered with us and hence making you CV available to them for furthur oppourtunities for you.So head back to Home Page and start creating you CV.
</p>
